text: Choi Su-bin (born ) is a South Korean female volleyball player. She is part of the South Korea women's national volleyball team. == Career == She participated in the 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Grand Champions Cup. == Clubs == * KGC Sports Club, 2017 == References == == External links == * FIVB Profile * Women Volleyball VII Grand Champions Cup 2017 Japan 05-10.09 +9 UTC - Winner China Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean women's volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Seoul
